title: [Orcswold, Wooded Trail]
description: Two large oak trees stand on either side of the trail, their branches forming a low arch over the mossy ground.  A flash of color in the intermittent sunlight shows that the overhanging foliage has been decorated with a variety of feathers and strange totems.
